summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 1, Block 5, Seattle Homestead Association First Addition, the north 67-63 feet of the west 110 feet of Lot 8, Block 51, Homecroft Addition, and Lots 4, 5 and 6, Block 1, Bailey's Addition to Georgetown, with respect to Use District, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 2-39.
